caption:
With Calvin Jones retiring from @parktoolblue I wanted to reshare the first time I met the legend himself just a couple of years ago. I showed him a silly bike “tool” I made to solve all my workshop woes, and he excitedly chatted with me even though I was one of hundreds of folks he had talked to that day in the booth at Sea Otter. He then said my 9 way wrench looked like a UFO from some sci-fi movie but now I can’t for the life of me remember what movie he mentioned. 😅

Long story short - meet your heros if you get the chance!
